      "parameters": {
        "content": "## INPUT CONTRACT (Execute Workflow Trigger)\n\n`action` (string): `ensureAndWrite|ensureSheet|writeRows` (default `ensureAndWrite`)\n`spreadsheetId` (string): existing spreadsheet ID (optional)\n`spreadsheetName` (string): spreadsheet title when creating (default `untitled-sheet`)\n`sheetName` (string): tab name (default `Sheet1`)\n`folderId` (string): Drive folder ID de move spreadsheet (optional)\n`rows` (2D array): data rows de ghi vao range\n`range` (string): range ghi du lieu (default `${sheetName}!A1`)\n`valueInputOption` (string): `RAW|USER_ENTERED` (default `RAW`)\n\n### Behavior flags (auto by Normalize Request)\n- `shouldEnsure`, `shouldWrite`, `shouldMove`\n- `shouldCreateSheet`, `shouldCallWriteApi`\n- `missingSpreadsheetIdForWrite`\n\n### Result keys\n`status`, `spreadsheetId`, `spreadsheetUrl`, `createStatusCode`, `writeStatusCode`, `writeRange`, `moveStatus`.",
